long_description: the country collection is a locally well-known shop from aucklanders, focusing on high-quality knitwear clothes exclusively made in new zealand. you will love the natural and unique fibres from merino wool as they own extreme resistance and irresistible comfort. our finest garments provide an authentic sense of new zealand's values, and our extensive collection displays an array of styles from classic and contemporary with luminous colours for ladies and gents. take advantage of our wide choice of accessories, such as beanies, scarves and gloves. this nz family-own store was established in 1989 and refurbished in 2019, maintaining a typical kiwi provincial atmosphere in a heritage building on the iconic queen street. visit us today
